sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Panel as Expo Admin Panel
    participant Auth as Firebase Authentication
    participant DB as Firestore Database
    participant Storage as Firebase Storage
    participant CF as Cloud Functions
    participant FCM as Cloud Messaging (FCM)

    Note over Admin, FCM: Admin Authentication
    Admin->>Panel: Enter Login Credentials
    Panel->>Auth: Authenticate Admin
    Auth-->>Panel: Authentication Success

    Note over Admin, FCM: View & Review Reports
    Admin->>Panel: Request Disaster Reports
    Panel->>DB: Fetch All Reports
    DB-->>Panel: Return Reports Data
    Admin->>Panel: View Community Vote Stats
    Panel->>DB: Fetch Vote Counts
    DB-->>Panel: Return Voting Results

    Note over Admin, FCM: Moderate Disaster Reports
    Admin->>Panel: Set Status (Verify / Resolve / False)
    Panel->>DB: Update Report Status Field
    DB->>CF: Trigger Status Change Logic
    CF->>FCM: Dispatch Notification to Relevant Users
    FCM-->>Panel: Notification Sent Confirmation

    Note over Admin, FCM: Media & User Management
    Admin->>Panel: Delete Misleading Media
    Panel->>Storage: Delete File
    Storage-->>Panel: Deletion Confirmed
    
    Admin->>Panel: Toggle User Access (Enable/Disable)
    Panel->>DB: Update User Account Status
    DB-->>Panel: Success Confirmation

    Note over Admin, FCM: Monitoring
    Admin->>Panel: Monitor Active SOS Events
    Panel->>DB: Fetch Recent SOS Records
    DB-->>Panel: Return SOS Data